releases:
- name: harbor-container-registry
  version: 1.10.1-build.7
addons:
- name: harbor-bosh-dns
  jobs:
  - name: harbor-dns-aliases
    release: harbor-container-registry
    properties:
      aliases:
        (( .properties.hostname.value )):
        - "*.harbor-app.(( ..harbor-container-registry.network_name )).(( ..harbor-container-registry.deployment_name )).bosh"
        (( .properties.auth_mode.selected_option.parsed_manifest(pks_uaa_fqdn) )):

- name: enable-bosh-dns
  jobs:
  - name: enable-bosh-dns
    release: harbor-container-registry
  include:
    deployments:
    - (( ..harbor-container-registry.deployment_name ))
